{"tid":1599590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多倫多市長拒絕出席中國國慶升旗儀式","createTime":"2019-09-28T05:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:30:57.000Z","uid":41404,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"250e199fd81df7e324ce1c7bbdf850e16f51f9b7","tid":1599590,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2019/09/27/john-tory-wont-attend-raising-of-chinese-flag-at-city-hall.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestar.com%2Fnews%2Fcity_hall%2F2019%2F09%2F27%2Fjohn-tory-wont-attend-raising-of-chinese-flag-at-city-hall.html&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=6c310301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2019/09/27/john-tory-wont-attend-raising-of-chinese-flag-at-city-hall.html</a>"},{"pid":"f56ee9fabc4b346431d8fa79eae631822b32b1f6","tid":1599590,"uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"Citing ongoing &ldquo;issues between Canada and China,&rdquo; Mayor John Tory is skipping the Sept. 30 raising of the Chinese flag at Toronto city hall&rsquo;s ceremonial flagpole.<br />\n<br />\nIn a statement Friday, Tory&rsquo;s office said he &ldquo;is hopeful that in the very near future a resolution will be found to a number of issues between Canada and China which are of great concern to him and to all of the people of Toronto, who strongly believe in addressing issues at home and abroad respectfully and with due process.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nLast year, Tory and Chinese consular officials helped hoist the Chinese flag up the ceremonial flagpole on city hall&rsquo;s green roof at a ceremony that included the Chinese anthem and lion-dancing. He tweeted photos of &ldquo;a day to celebrate the rich culture &amp; achievements of the country and its people. Wishing Toronto&rsquo;s Chinese community a happy National Day.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThis year&rsquo;s flag-raising has special significance, the city website notes, as a celebration of the &ldquo;70th anniversary of the founding of the People&rsquo;s Republic of China.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"1763ffdf9ed09e91ffc76e4a2083164d7d2852bb","tid":1599590,"uid":218158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"We Connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf1a733fd39b1f7aa2e48d76b2c011e84c30197","tid":1599590,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"Well done Aussies"},{"pid":"7c157a7dc5665723ca3547a414b3545bcc4778d0","tid":1599590,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edf1a733fd39b1f7aa2e48d76b2c011e84c30197","tid":1599590,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"Well done Aussies"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"Aussies<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f79388f612525080cb55f728b219059afd2763","tid":1599590,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c157a7dc5665723ca3547a414b3545bcc4778d0","tid":1599590,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edf1a733fd39b1f7aa2e48d76b2c011e84c30197","tid":1599590,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"Well done Aussies"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"Aussies<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gi